    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Geometrical diagrams used as an aid to worship or meditation in tantric traditions. The assumed benefits to the user are derived from Hindu pantheon and tantric texts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
